addTree

public boolean addTree(Tree tree)
Scaffolding code that does two things:
  1. Adds tree to this TreeSet's constituent Trees.
  2. Adds this TreeSet to tree 's TreeSets.
So it takes care of both sides of the TreeSet<-> Tree relationship.

This method assumes that tree is not in a Hibernate-detached state.

Parameters:
tree - see description
Returns:
true if this set did not already contain tree

protected TreeSet resetPPodVersionInfo()
Description copied from class: PPodEntity
